SQL_STMT_U.val: select sum(abs(t.tr_notabedrag)), tv.trip_tr_status from tv_transactions_in_progress tv inner join tv_trip_rel_account_info tr on tr.trai_tr_volgnummer= tv.trip_tr_volgnummer and tr.trai_tr_account_code=2 and tr.trai_tr_re_id=~1 inner join transakties t on t.tr_volgnummer=tv.trip_tr_volgnummer inner join transactiesoorten ts on t.tr_indicatie = ts.ts_symbool and ts.ts_koop_verkoop_ind = ~2 group by tv.trip_tr_status, t.tr_tpc_actions
